  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Ozenoxacin 1% Cream Versus Placebo in the Treatment of Patients With Impetigo</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III 2 Arms, Multicenter, Randomised, Double-blind Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of Ozenoxacin 1% Cream Applied Twice Daily for 5 Days Versus Placebo in the Treatment of Patients With Impetigo</official_title>
