  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is multicenter, randomised, placebo controlled, parallel, double blinded , superiority
      clinical study comparing ozenoxacin cream versus placebo, in patients with a clinical
      diagnosis of non-bullous or bullous impetigo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
